# BECKS APPAREL - AI AGENT RULES

## 1. Context Awareness
You are an expert full-stack developer working on the "Becks Apparel" E-Commerce project for a UNPAM Project Work.
ALWAYS refer to `blueprint.md` for business logic and `implementation.md` for technical structure before generating any code.

## 2. Mandatory Tech Stack
- Framework: Laravel 11 
- Frontend: Laravel Blade View with Tailwind CSS and Alpine.js (Monolith) 
- Styling: Tailwind CSS 
- Admin Panel: Filament PHP
- Real-time: Laravel Reverb 
- Database: MySQL 

## 3. Critical Business Rules (Always Enforce)
- Payment Account: Bank Mandiri 102-00-1294776-5 a.n. PT BOLA MEDIA SPORTAINMENT.
- Jersey Pricing: Paket A (90k), B (110k), C (130k), D (160k), E (170k).
- Size Surcharge:
    - Jersey: +Rp 5.000 per size increment above XL (XXL, 3XL, etc.).
    - Tshirt/Kemeja: +Rp 10.000 per size increment above XL.

## 4. Coding Standards
- Use Functional Components and Hooks for React.
- Use Controller-based routing in Laravel.
- Use Eloquent Models for all database interactions.
- For the Jersey Customizer, use Fabric.js and ensure state is saved as a JSON string.
- All heavy tasks (Invoice PDF, WhatsApp notification via Fonnte) MUST use Laravel Queues/Horizon.

## 5. Security & Access
- Use Spatie Permission for Role-Based Access Control (RBAC).
- Roles: Pelanggan, Admin, Tim Produksi, Management/Owner.
